text: Baatarkhuyagiin Otgonbold (born 20 December 1996) is a Mongolian archer. Otgonbold competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Baatarkhuyag OtgonboldOtgonbold BAATARKHUYAG == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia
